import React from "react"; import "../css/Main.css"; import Background from "../resources/cityscape_fin.png"; import * as Tone from 'tone' export const Synthesizer = () => { function handleKey(e){ const synth = new Tone.Synth().toDestination(); const now = Tone.now(); var key = ""; if(e.currentTarget.className === "black-key"){ e.stopPropagation(); console.log("Clicked " + e.currentTarget.textContent); key = e.currentTarget.textContent; } else{ console.log("Clicked " + e.currentTarget.textContent[e.currentTarget.textContent.length -1]); key = e.currentTarget.textContent[e.currentTarget.textContent.length -1]; } switch (key) { // LEFT ROW case "z": return synth.triggerAttackRelease("C3", now); case "s": return synth.triggerAttackRelease("C#3", now); case "x": return synth.triggerAttackRelease("D3", now); case "d": return synth.triggerAttackRelease("D#3", now); case "c": return synth.triggerAttackRelease("E3", now); case "v": return synth.triggerAttackRelease("F3", now); case "g": return synth.triggerAttackRelease("F#3", now); case "b": return synth.triggerAttackRelease("G3", now); case "h": return synth.triggerAttackRelease("G#3", now); case "n": return synth.triggerAttackRelease("A3", now); case "j": return synth.triggerAttackRelease("A#3", now); case "m": return synth.triggerAttackRelease("B3", now); // RIGHT ROW case "q": return synth.triggerAttackRelease("C4", now); case "2": return synth.triggerAttackRelease("C#4", now); case "w": return synth.triggerAttackRelease("D4", now); case "3": return synth.triggerAttackRelease("D#4", now); case "e": return synth.triggerAttackRelease("E4", now); case "r": return synth.triggerAttackRelease("F4", now); case "5": return synth.triggerAttackRelease("F#4", now); case "t": return synth.triggerAttackRelease("G4", now); case "6": return synth.triggerAttackRelease("G#4", now); case "y": return synth.triggerAttackRelease("A4", now); case "7": return synth.triggerAttackRelease("A#4", now); case "u": return synth.triggerAttackRelease("B4", now); default: return; } } return ( <>
